title: Inside Out 2 | Teaser Trailer
tags: Pixar|Disney|Disney Pixar|Pixar Movie|Animation
description: üößThings are getting messyüößDisney and Pixar's #InsideOut2 is coming to theaters June 2024 with brand new emotions!The little voices inside Riley‚Äôs head know her inside and out‚Äîbut next summer, everything changes when Disney and Pixar‚Äôs ‚ÄúInside Out 2‚Äù introduces a new Emotion: Anxiety. According to director Kelsey Mann, the new character promises to stir things up within headquarters. ‚ÄúAnxiety, voiced by Maya Hawke, might be new to the crew, but she‚Äôs not really the type to take a back seat,‚Äù said Mann. ‚ÄúThat makes a lot of sense if you think about it in terms of what goes on inside all our minds.‚Äù A trailer, poster and film stills are now available for what promises to be the feel-good (or feel-everything) film of Summer 2024. Disney and Pixar‚Äôs ‚ÄúInside Out 2‚Äù returns to the mind of newly minted teenager Riley just as headquarters is undergoing a sudden demolition to make room for something entirely unexpected: new Emotions! Joy, Sadness, Anger, Fear and Disgust, who‚Äôve long been running a successful operation by all accounts, aren‚Äôt sure how to feel when Anxiety shows up. And it looks like she‚Äôs not alone. Maya Hawke lends her voice to Anxiety, alongside Amy Poehler as Joy, Phyllis Smith as Sadness, Lewis Black as Anger, Tony Hale as Fear, and Liza Lapira as Disgust. Directed by Kelsey Mann and produced by Mark Nielsen, ‚ÄúInside Out 2‚Äù releases only in theaters Summer 2024.

title: I Crossed The World's Deadliest Jungle: Darien Gap
tags: DARIEN|Darien jungle|migrants|venezuela|snake pass|elon musk|bald and bankrupt|Timmy karter|south america|adventure|travel|journalism|documentary
description: The Darien Gap known as the world's most dangerous jungle. I had heard of the Darien many years ago through National Geographic and it had both fascinated and intimidated me. I knew one day I would have to visit...When the word Darien started appearing in the news in recent years by way of the migrant crises I decided that now was the time to explore it for myself. And so myself and my good friend @TimmyKarter headed north from Medellin in search of a way across the infamous jungle, avoiding cartel and bandits, injury and tropical diseases, on an adventure with migrants from all over the world where national laws don't apply. Only the laws of the jungle.Join us as we enter...the Darien.

Survival depends on your ability to defend yourself!...and more!We'll be adding more and more to Space Trash Scavenger, so be sure to wishlist and follow for updates! title: Richard Hammond drives a Rimac for the first time since his life-threatening crash
tags: jeremy clarkson|richard hammond|james may|top gear|the grand tour|drivetribe|Richard Hammond crash|Hammond crash|Rimac|Hammond Rimac|Rimac nevera

description: Now and Then's eventful journey to fruition took place over five decades and is the product of conversations and collaborations between the four Beatles that go on to this day. The long mythologised John Lennon demo was first worked on in February 1995 by Paul, George and Ringo as part of The Beatles Anthology project but it remained unfinished, partly because of the impossible technological challenges involved in working with the vocal John had recorded on tape in the 1970s. For years it looked like the song could never be completed. But in 2022 there was a stroke of serendipity. A software system developed by Peter Jackson and his team, used throughout the production of the documentary series Get Back, finally opened the way for the uncoupling of John‚Äôs vocal from his piano part. As a result, the original recording could be brought to life and worked on anew with contributions from all four Beatles. This remarkable story of musical archaeology reflects The Beatles‚Äô endless creative curiosity and shared fascination with technology. It marks the completion of the last recording that John, Paul and George and Ringo will get to make together and celebrates the legacy of the foremost and most influential band in popular music history.Video Director: Peter JacksonVideo Producers: Peter Jackson, Clare Olssen, Jonathan ClydeAudio Producers: Paul McCartney and Giles MartinProduction Company: WingNut Films Productions LtdOrder/Listen to Now And Then: https://TheBeatles.lnk.to/NowAndThenYTOrder/Listen to Red and Blue: https://TheBeatles.lnk.to/RedAndBlue2023YTWatch more videos from The Beatles: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/YTPlaylists Subscribe to The Beatles‚Äô YouTube channel & ring the bell to never miss a new video: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/YTSignup Sign up for The Beatles‚Äô Official Email List: https://www.thebeatles.com/newsletter   Stream The Beatles: üéôÔ∏è Apple Music: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/AppleMusic üéôÔ∏è Spotify: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/Spotify üéôÔ∏è Amazon Music: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/AmazonMusic üéôÔ∏è Pandora: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/Pandora üéôÔ∏è Tidal: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/Tidal üéôÔ∏è Deezer: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/Deezer üéôÔ∏è YouTube Music: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/YouTubeMusic   Follow The Beatles:  ‚≠ê https://www.thebeatles.com ‚≠ê https://www.instagram.com/thebeatles‚≠ê https://www.facebook.com/thebeatles‚≠ê https://www.tiktok.com/@thebeatles‚≠ê https://twitter.com/thebeatles #TheBeatles #NowAndThen #JohnLennon #PaulMcCartney #GeorgeHarrison #RingoStarr

title: the end of this chapter (important announcement)
tags: [none]
description: I started developing the Sunee App and brand in 2018, at a time where my career and building my business was my main focus and drive. Before I was a mother and a wife I felt such a sense of purpose and passion pouring all of my time into work.Now in 2023, a lot has changed. Priorities have shifted, business goals have been refined and most importantly, I have become a wife and a mother. This season of motherhood has been my greatest blessing and an experience I know is fleeting. In our life there is time to do everything, but not all at once. With all of this in mind and my intentions to create more balance in my life, I have come to the decision to close down the Sunee App. When I work on a project or product, I will give it my all and nothing less. Considering all avenues and possibilities for the app's future, the decision to close the app has been one that has given me the greatest sense of peace.In saying this, this has not been a decision I have made lightly as I know how special and impactful Sunee and our recipes are to so many of you. I want to take this moment to sincerely thank every single one of you who have supported Sunee. None of this would have been possible without you and I‚Äôm so grateful that you have been along for this amazing journey!While the app will no longer exist, this is not goodbye. My passion for creating healthy recipes is deeper than ever, however, my approach and pace will now honour my season. The experience of creating my cookbook was the confirmation I needed to acknowledge that right now in my life, I need to be working on a project basis.. This allows me to pour all of my creativity into my work, whilst prioritising my role as a mother and raising my boys.Again, thank you all for your support and love.For more details on the closure of the Sunee app head to www.sunee.com/closing

Box Jenny Appleford7211 Haven Ave, Unit E-407Rancho Cucamonga, CA 91701Kyle‚Äôs Channel:https://www.youtube.com/@kyleapple9702INSTAGRAM: jenny_applefordFACEBOOK: Our Brave Jenny For business inquiries: veganapplefords@gmail.com DIAGNOSIS:March 19th, 2021 Stage IIIA Non Small Cell Lung Cancer (Non-Smoking)February 2022 Stage IV Non Small Cell Lung Cancer (spreading to Brain, and other parts of lung and lymph nodes)Gene Mutation EGFR with Exon 20 InsertionTREATMENTS: Received or currently Receiving2021: 8 Rounds of Chemotherapy (Carboplatin and Paclitaxel) with 30 concurrent radiation treatments to chest and lungFailed Immunotherapy directly after Chemo and Radiation (Durvalumab, 1 round)2022: Chemotherapy10 rounds of Chemotherapy (Carboplatin, Alimta, and Avastin) 6 with Carboplatin, 4 withoutTargeted Brain Radiation (Completed)CURRENT TREATMENT:I am on a clinical trial for my specific gene mutation Our GoFundMe Link:https://gofund.me/5edf81e5The purpose of my channel is to document my cancer journey to look back on, and/or help anyone else going through anything similar. It is also to potentially help loved ones supporting those who are in this fight as well. This is also an easy way to update a lot of people at once. My main goal is to have footage of this journey for my husband and children to look back on. I originally created this channel as a sort of video diary for my family. title: The Beatles - Now And Then (Official Audio)
tags: [none]
description: Now and Then's eventful journey to fruition took place over five decades and is the product of conversations and collaborations between the four Beatles that go on to this day. The long mythologised John Lennon demo was first worked on in February 1995 by Paul, George and Ringo as part of The Beatles Anthology project but it remained unfinished, partly because of the impossible technological challenges involved in working with the vocal John had recorded on tape in the 1970s. For years it looked like the song could never be completed. But in 2022 there was a stroke of serendipity. A software system developed by Peter Jackson and his team, used throughout the production of the documentary series Get Back, finally opened the way for the uncoupling of John‚Äôs vocal from his piano part. As a result, the original recording could be brought to life and worked on anew with contributions from all four Beatles. This remarkable story of musical archaeology reflects The Beatles‚Äô endless creative curiosity and shared fascination with technology. It marks the completion of the last recording that John, Paul and George and Ringo will get to make together and celebrates the legacy of the foremost and most influential band in popular music history.Order/Listen to Now And Then: https://TheBeatles.lnk.to/NowAndThenYTOrder/Listen to 'Red' and 'Blue': https://TheBeatles.lnk.to/RedAndBlue2023YT Watch more videos from The Beatles: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/YTPlaylistsSubscribe to The Beatles‚Äô YouTube channel & ring the bell to never miss a new video: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/YTSignupSign up for The Beatles‚Äô Official Email List: https://www.thebeatles.com/newsletter Stream The Beatles:üéôÔ∏è Apple Music: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/AppleMusicüéôÔ∏è Spotify: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/SpotifyüéôÔ∏è Amazon Music: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/AmazonMusicüéôÔ∏è Pandora: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/PandoraüéôÔ∏è Tidal: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/TidalüéôÔ∏è Deezer: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/DeezerüéôÔ∏è YouTube Music: https://thebeatles.lnk.to/stream/YouTubeMusic Follow The Beatles:‚≠ê https://www.thebeatles.com‚≠ê https://www.instagram.com/thebeatles‚≠ê https://www.facebook.com/thebeatles‚≠ê https://www.tiktok.com/@thebeatles‚≠ê https://twitter.com/thebeatles #TheBeatles #NowAndThen #JohnLennon #PaulMcCartney #GeorgeHarrison #RingoStarr
